{"tid":825396,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"Apple Watch 一件關注你的健康的數碼產品","createTime":"2018-09-17T13:54:05.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-17T14:58:45.000Z","uid":121146,"like":2,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"bcbab5ac784b96a444b3c7686c6c8d037fa9312e","tid":825396,"uid":121146,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-17T13:54:05.000Z","msg":"很多人沒有做身體檢查的習慣，而心電圖是其中一項常進行的測試。現在 Apple Watch Series 4 可幫你做心電圖，加上透過分析你的心跳速度，及早作出提示，減少因疏忽而沒有及早處理心臟問題。有了 Apple Watch Series 4，相信可以令心臟有問題的人及早求醫。<br />\n<br />\n智能手錶以往只關心的都是外型、通知功能、電池持航力等元素。其次關心的就是你的運動數據。偉大的產品跟普通的產品是有很大的分別，不是功能也不是售價，而是定位。今天筆者從 Apple Watch Series 4 中感受得 Apple 的用心，很久沒有這種感動出現過。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.newmobilelife.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/fall.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.newmobilelife.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2018%2F09%2Ffall.png&h=6c86bc1a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.newmobilelife.com/2018/09/13/apple-watch-series4-with-heart/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.newmobilelife.com%2F2018%2F09%2F13%2Fapple-watch-series4-with-heart%2F&d=8xrTX4oEgcXVd4BAtBD8AAtTNu1qqkxUxYmVHECffP4%3D&h=70bcad24\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.newmobilelife.com/2018/09/13/apple-watch-series4-with-heart/</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n蘋果  謝謝你的用心    因為直至 Series 3以前 這種「用心」 原來都未出現過 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />   <br />\n買 Series 4之前果d即係傻仔 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"39e0565f9b77d24f7cb9d825ab1d5f2287f1367e","tid":825396,"uid":132587,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-17T13:57:08.000Z","msg":"Apple Watch Series 4 心電圖功能 美國率先提供 其他市場未有定案"},{"pid":"afa59933b14ddbc565b74ccae6b3922504612cc3","tid":825396,"uid":121146,"like":2,"dislike":3,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"39e0565f9b77d24f7cb9d825ab1d5f2287f1367e","tid":825396,"uid":132587,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-17T13:57:08.000Z","msg":"Apple Watch Series 4 心電圖功能 美國率先提供 其他市場未有定案"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-17T13:58:23.000Z","msg":"即係其他國家買4都係傻仔 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"319b38e52b5e23270fa98a34b7d96805c6b95786","tid":825396,"uid":168366,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-17T14:58:45.000Z","msg":"心跳關注不嬲都有架啦<br />\n1-3代都已經救返唔少人<br />\n唔知你有咩好笑"}]}